---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Prose from '../../components/Prose.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Support — Porthole" lang="en">
  <Prose title="Support">
    <p class="text-sm text-muted">An unofficial Telegram viewer for Apple TV</p>

    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-muted">Contact</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:szlab.ai@outlook.com">szlab.ai@outlook.com</a></p>
    <p>We usually reply within a few business days. Please include your Apple TV model and tvOS version.</p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>How do I sign in?</h3>
    <p>Porthole uses your existing Telegram account. On first launch, enter your phone number and the login code Telegram sends you. Porthole never sees or stores your password.</p>

    <h3>How do I report or block content?</h3>
    <p>Open a message and use its action menu to <em>Report</em> or <em>Block</em>, or leave a chat. Objectionable content can also be reported to us by email.</p>

    <h3>What do I need to run Porthole?</h3>
    <p>An Apple TV running tvOS 17 or later, and a Telegram account.</p>

    <h3>Is this the official Telegram app?</h3>
    <p>No. Porthole is an independent, unofficial client and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Telegram.</p>

    <h2>Report Objectionable Content</h2>
    <p>Use the in-app report/block controls, or email <a href="mailto:szlab.ai@outlook.com">szlab.ai@outlook.com</a> with details. We act on reports promptly.</p>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>
